{
  "stem": "12003.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember that my father did go to war when Poland went to war with Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't come right away back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember when we were bombed, when the shells were dropping on us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember being in bomb shelters and saying the Shema Yisrael.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what it meant, but my aunt, my mother, everybody says, children pray, whoever knows how to pray.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember sitting in this bomb shelters and praying, Shema Yisrael.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- I don't how long we didn't see our father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The word came that yes, he was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, he appeared in his civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were told, the children, not to tell anyone, not even the neighbors, that he is back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I guess he was a Polish officer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if the word would get out to the Germans that he-- Polish officer is back at that time-- that was before the Jewish situation with the armbands and-- and stopping us from going to schools.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But knowing that he was an officer, they might take him away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So for a while, he couldn't go out, and he didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember our uncles and aunts were coming to us, and some other people, to visit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Little by little, I guess, he went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, before we went to ghetto, I remember the pious Hasidic Jews being rushed down through the streets, one side of their faces and the heads being shaved, and with their hands up.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were being run through the streets, followed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Poles used to stand on the sides, applaud, and laugh.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
